### Get Current User
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Update Profile
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "phoneNumber": "1234567890",
  "dateOfBirth": "1995-01-01",
  "address": "123 Street",
  "city": "Karachi",
  "state": "Sindh",
  "country": "Pakistan",
  "postalCode": "75500"
}

### Partial Update Profile
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "0987654321"
}

### Delete Account
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me?password=StrongPass123
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Change Password
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me/password
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "StrongPass123",
  "newPassword": "NewStrongPass123",
  "confirmPassword": "NewStrongPass123"
}

### Get User Settings
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me/settings
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Update User Settings
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me/settings
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "emailNotifications": true,
  "smsNotifications": true,
  "pushNotifications": true,
  "transactionNotifications": true,
  "securityNotifications": true,
  "marketingNotifications": false,
  "language": "en",
  "currency": "PKR",
  "timeZone": "Asia/Karachi",
  "theme": "dark",
  "profileVisibility": "public",
  "showEmail": true,
  "showPhone": true
}

### Upload Avatar
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me/avatar
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="avatar.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./avatar.png
--boundary--

### Remove Avatar
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me/avatar
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Enable MFA
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me/mfa/enable
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Disable MFA
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me/mfa/disable
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "StrongPass123"
}

### Verify MFA
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me/mfa/verify
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "otp": "123456"
}

### Get Notifications
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me/notifications?unreadOnly=true&pageable.page=0&pageable.size=10
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Mark Notification as Read
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me/notifications/1/read
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Mark All Notifications as Read
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Unread Notification Count
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me/notifications/unread/count
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get User Activities
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me/activities?pageable.page=0&pageable.size=10
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/health
